## ButLast type

Extracts everything except the last element from a tuple.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type ButLast<T extends unknown[], C extends unknown[] = []> = {
    0: ButLast<Tail<T>, Prepend<Head<T>, C>>;
    1: Reverse<C>;
}[IsEmpty<Tail<T>>];
```
